info.name: GovInfo Search Service
info.description:
This search service Postman collection allows a quick import and test of several main search service functions, including examples of pagination, historical, and resultLevel parameters.

This includes a sampling of examples as requested by users in https://www.github.com/usgpo/api/issues/1

item.description: This set of requests demonstrates basic functionality of the API using the BUDGET collection, because it has a small sample size as well as historical and current versions. Modifying this set of requests should be done with the understanding that some of the requests are chained - e.g. Basic Search - collection is used as a baseline for Basic Search- historical=true and Basic Search- historical=true nextPage
